=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Reference_Assignment_ex4 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 232 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally sparse.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: sparse
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 232.4091
  harmonic_decay_rate: -12.4635
  harmonic_regularity: 0.7782
  pitch_clarity: 94.8765
  inharmonicity: 0.0095
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -18.7798
  resonance_freq: 172.2656

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Assignment Statements Example 4
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Reference/Assignment.html
// Tags: Assignment, Reference
// ---
// --- Example 4 ---
(
{
    var sig;
    sig = SinOsc.ar(LFNoise0.kr(10).exprange(1, 1000));
    sig = SinOsc.ar(310, sig * 3);
    sig = SinOsc.ar(230, sig * 0.4);
    sig * 0.2
}.play
)
